HEADWORD: Matico
<hw>Ma*ti"co</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
Peruvian plant (<spn>Piperelongatum</spn> or <spn>Artanthe
elongatum</spn>), allied to the pepper, the leaves of which are used as
a styptic and astringent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

